```plantuml
@startuml Cpanchal1_Chatbot101-with-AWS-Lambda

actor User as U
participant "Webex Teams" as WT
participant "API Gateway" as APIG
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "chatbot.py" as Chatbot
participant "icanhazdadjoke.com" as JokeAPI

U -> WT: Mention Bot
WT -> APIG: Send Webhook Event
APIG -> Lambda: Trigger Function
Lambda -> Chatbot: Invoke main()
Chatbot -> Chatbot: getJoke()
Chatbot -> JokeAPI: HTTP GET Request
JokeAPI -> Chatbot: JSON Response with Joke
Chatbot -> Chatbot: postJoke()
Chatbot -> WT: Post Joke to Room
Chatbot -> Lambda: Return Success Message
Lambda -> APIG: Response to Webhook
APIG -> WT: Acknowledge Event

@enduml
```